{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be rustic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EcoThreads</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f1ea;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #2a4d69;\n            color: #f4f1ea;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #8097b5;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 10px;\n            background-color: #4c7294;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #2a4d69;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #f4f1ea;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #a5b9c9;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            background-color: #8097b5;\n            color: #f4f1ea;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n        .section h3 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: #2a4d69;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #8097b5;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .products {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        .product-item {\n            width: 30%;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #d3caca;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: #fcfbf8;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .product-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .product-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .product-item h4 {\n            margin: 10px 0;\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            color: #2a4d69;\n        }\n        .product-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n        }\n        .product-item .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #4c7294;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .about-text {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            background-color: #2a4d69;\n            color: #f4f1ea;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>EcoThreads</h1>\n        <p>Sustainable Style, Naturally</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#products\">Products</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Embrace Conscious Fashion</h2>\n        <p>Discover our collection of beautifully crafted apparel made from the finest organic and recycled materials. Feel good, look good, do good.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Our Story</h3>\n            <p class=\"about-text\">\n                At EcoThreads, we believe that fashion can be both beautiful and responsible. We are dedicated to creating timeless pieces that not only enhance your style but also minimize our impact on the planet. From sourcing ethical materials to ensuring fair labor practices, every step of our process is guided by a commitment to sustainability.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"products\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Our Collection</h3>\n            <div class=\"products\">\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/8097b5/ffffff?text=Organic+Tee\" alt=\"Organic Cotton T-Shirt\">\n                    <h4>Organic Cotton Tee</h4>\n                    <p>Soft, breathable, and made from 100% certified organic cotton.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$45.00</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4c7294/ffffff?text=Recycled+Denim\" alt=\"Recycled Denim Jeans\">\n                    <h4>Recycled Denim Jeans</h4>\n                    <p>Classic fit jeans crafted from post-consumer recycled denim.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$90.00</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2a4d69/ffffff?text=Linen+Dress\" alt=\"Linen Sundress\">\n                    <h4>Linen Sundress</h4>\n                    <p>Lightweight and airy linen dress, perfect for warmer days.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$120.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n            <p class=\"about-text\">\n                We'd love to hear from you! For inquiries or to learn more about our sustainable practices, please reach out to us.\n                <br><br>\n                Email: info@ecothreads.com\n                <br>\n                Follow us on social media!\n            </p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 EcoThreads. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}